PRIME MINISTER 'S SECRETARIAT
Shri Govind Ballath Pant, Minister of Home
Affairs, is appointed to hold charge, in addition, of
the Ministry of Heavy Industries.
2.
Shri T.T.Krishnamachari, at present Minister
of Commerce & Industry and Iron & Steel, will relinquish
charge of the Ministry of Commerce & Industry and take
charge of the Ministry of Finance in its place from the
Prime Minister..
ERM
350 copies.
3.

and Supply, is appointed to hold charge, in addition,
of the Ministry of Commerce & Consumer Industries.
Sd/- J.Nehru.
